* overlay:

   * create overlay/src/<name>

   * maybe add <name> to DEFAULT_OVERLAYS in overlay/Makefile

* buildroot:

   * add BR2_PACKAGE_FISCHSTAEBCHEN_OVERLAY_<NAME> to buildroot/package/fischstaebchen/Config.in

   * add <NAME> to buildroot/package/fischstaebchen/fischstaebchen.mk (in FISCHSTAEBCHEN_DO_GEN_OVERLAYS_LIST)

* standalone:

   * maybe add <name> to INITRAMFS_OVERLAYS in standalone/overlay.mk
